	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Christus, servator unicus, velit hunc annum et tibi et tuis esse felicissimum.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratias ago pro scriptis; schedam remitto, ut iubebas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutabis d. legatum et precaberis ipsi felicissimum annum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dudum audivi graves fuisse concertationes inter cardinales <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1060" cert="high">Mantuanum</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1291" cert="high">Turnonium</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de" type="auto">So hör ich wol: der drittman mit der däschen ist darzwüschen gekummen und fürt die brut heym.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Der Tüffel zerryß imm die däschen und den stuͦl; das ist min glückwünschen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Reliquit ei grandem pecuniam frater mortuus, marchio <persName type="auto_name">Müssiae</persName>, per quam nunc potuit mercari sedem pestilentiae.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quoniam vero multi ei invident, mox tolletur veneno.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Aber aller tüffel namen: sy sind doch bessers nitt wärt.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">- <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Claronensis</placeName> controversia adhuc ita haeret: legati <placeName ref="l2448" cert="high">5 Pagorum</placeName> responderunt se nihil accepisse in mandatis, velle autem ea, quae proposuerint illi, referre domum efficereque, si possint, ut proximis comitiis 4. februarii <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l21" cert="high">Badae</placeName> celebrandis respondeatur.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Reliquae Cantones serio mandarunt, ne quid interim vi aut manu armata tentent.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="manual"><foreign xml:lang="de">So ist's noch im kunst:</foreign> Dominus orandus est sedulo, ut frangat cruenta et impia impiorum consilia.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Veneti forte foedus ambient; audio enim ipsos sibi a <persName type="auto_name">Philippo</persName> metuere et a <persName type="auto_name">Sabaudo</persName>.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De literis tuis, ne aliquando tibi accersant periculum, iubeo te esse securum; si posthac ullas aboleri volueris, subsigna ad finem: "Crema."</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Wers dann lese, wurd meinen, der brieff wer geschriben von <placeName ref="l104" cert="high">Cremona</placeName> etc.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed quod modo dixi, nolo te esse solicitum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Der guͦt, fromm schuldheyß <persName type="citizen_name">Weyß</persName> ist uns der tagen ouch gestorben.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vive et vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Festinavi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> 5. ianuarii 1560.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="de" type="manual"><foreign xml:lang="la">Mei omnes te et tuos salutant</foreign> und wünschend üch ein guͦt jar.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8009" cert="high">Ioanni Fabritio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiensis</placeName> ecclesiae ministro fideli, domino et fratri charissimo suo.</s>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l98" cert="high">Chur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
